{"TopicId":119664,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Mouse cursor offset ( misaligned cursor )","CreatedByName":"Noumex","CreatedById":111583,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-29T15:34:21Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Noumex","CreatedById":111583,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-29T15:34:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMy config:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E- \u003Cstrong\u003EUnmodded Kerbal\u003C/strong\u003E, \u003Cstrong\u003ESTEAM \u003C/strong\u003Einstall, up to date I guess\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E- \u003Cstrong\u003EWindows 7 32 bits\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E- STEAM startup parameters: \u003Cstrong\u003E-force-opengl\u003C/strong\u003E (otherwise it crashes while loading )\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E- Windows display has 100% font scale, not the 125% or custom scale (I\u0027ve read an issue about this on other games, my config seams safe here)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMy problem:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003EThe \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003Emouse cursor is displayed on the right of the actual cursor position\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E for the game.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis offset is important enough to mess with the interface and so I have unreachable icons or buttons.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOf course this misalignment is also globally disturbing.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ve googled this topic, and tried the \u0022no resize for high dpi\u0022 option on .exe, with no luck.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPlease, can anyone help ?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"reinderien","CreatedById":154355,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-10T03:52:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222150871\u