reatedByName":"reinderien","CreatedById":154355,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T02:12:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222749458\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022119664\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473501826\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002216426\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/09/2016 at 6:03 AM, sal_vager said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a rather old thread \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/154355-reinderien/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022154355\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/154355-reinderien/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@reinderien\u003C/a\u003E, so it\u0027s unlikely the same cause.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOK, that\u0027s fine. Anyway, I found a workaround. The in-game resolution seemed odd and didn\u0027t match what it should have for native LCD full-screen, so I fixed it and it solved the issue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}